data.description: Stunning home in LAUREL MOUNTAIN RANCH. Looking for room? Looking for storage? This home has you covered! As you enter, you'll experience the formal dining area, which flows into the family room. Next, you'll notice the sprawling kitchen space right behind the family room. Cabinets galore!  Imagine preparing the next meal easily and quickly because everything you need is where it belongs!  Upstairs you'll find a multi-use room to the right, office, playroom, game room, whatever you need with closet space to spare. To the left is the master suite: so much room and lovely design features in the architecture. You'll find two sink areas, and a separate tub and shower. Walk-in closets again give you a lot of storage.  A covered back patio with lots of room waits for you out back.  The seller has loved this home so much and hopes you do too.
